11 CarLink::CarLink(ros::NodeHandle *const nh, const int car_num, const int pin) :
12  nh{nh},
13  car_num{car_num},
14  topic{String("car") + String(car_num) + String("/effort")},
15  throttle_throw{0},
16  steering_center{1500},
17  steering_left{1500},
18  steering_right{1500},
19  enabled{false},
20  ppm_out{RISING},
21  effort_sub{topic.c_str(), &CarLink::effort_cb, this} {
22  ppm_out.write(THROTTLE_CHANNEL, THROTTLE_ZERO);
23  ppm_out.write(STEERING_CHANNEL, steering_center);
24  ppm_out.begin(pin);
25  this->nh->subscribe(effort_sub);
26 }

30 }

36 void CarLink::disable() {
37  ppm_out.write(THROTTLE_CHANNEL, THROTTLE_ZERO);
38  enabled = false;

41 bool CarLink::update_params() {
42  if (nh->connected()
43  && nh->getParam((String("~car") + String(car_num) + String("/throttle_throw")).c_str(), &throttle_throw)
44  && nh->getParam((String("~car") + String(car_num) + String("/steering_center")).c_str(), &steering_center)
45  && nh->getParam((String("~car") + String(car_num) + String("/steering_left")).c_str(), &steering_left)
46  && nh->getParam((String("~car") + String(car_num) + String("/steering_right")).c_str(), &steering_right)) {
47  return true;
48  } else {
49  throttle_throw = 0;
50  steering_center = 1500;
51  steering_left = 1500;
52  steering_right = 1500;
53  return false;
54  }
55 }
56 
57 void CarLink::effort_cb(const rktl_msgs::ControlEffort& effort) {
58  // throttle
59  if (enabled) {
60  ppm_out.write(THROTTLE_CHANNEL, THROTTLE_ZERO + throttle_throw * effort.throttle);
61  } else {
62  ppm_out.write(THROTTLE_CHANNEL, THROTTLE_ZERO);
63  }
64 
65  // steering
66  if (effort.steering > 0) {
67  ppm_out.write(STEERING_CHANNEL, steering_center + (steering_left - steering_center) * effort.steering);
68  } else if (effort.steering < 0) {
69  ppm_out.write(STEERING_CHANNEL, steering_center + (steering_center - steering_right) * effort.steering);
70  } else {
71  ppm_out.write(STEERING_CHANNEL, steering_center);
72  }
73 }
